movie_name: Smile for the Dead: An Examination of Spirit Photography
short_description: Uncovers the eerie mystery of William H. Mumler's spirit photography and his ghostly portraits of the1800s. This documentary investigates Mumler's techniques and why society so needed him in the post-Civil War era.
